nodes.text: Che-Yuan Wang is credited for Level Editor and Gameplay Programming on Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II. He did also do some work on Star Wars: DroidWorks and Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Mysteries of the Sith. Che-Yuan participated in other LucasArts titles such as Wikipedia:Grim Fandango and Wikipedia:Indiana Jones and the Infernal Machine.
